Name: Financial CS Subscribers

Caption.String: For each subscriber class, assign a share of the system in Year 1 with an annual growth rate, or click Value/Sched and Edit to assign a share for each year.

Tool Tip.String: Type a name for Subscriber Class 1, for example Anchor, Commercial, Residential, LMI, etc.
Click Value/Sched to switch between a single value with a growth rate and annual values over the analysis period.

Description.String: Enter a subscriber share of system for each year.
